1 the core values he has instilled in the department he runs: character, integrity, knowledge,
2 stewardship, and competitiveness; and
3 WHEREAS, this honorable body congratulates Mitch Barnhart for his many
4 accomplishments as athletic director at UK and commends him for his dedication to the
5 student-athletes and to the future of college athletics;
6 NOW, THEREFORE,
7 Be it resolved by the Senate of the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of
8 Kentucky:
9 Section 1. The members of the Senate hereby honor UK Athletic Director
10 Mitch Barnhart upon his retirement.
11 Section 2. When the Senate adjourns this day, it does so in honor of Mitch
12 Barnhart.
13 Section 3. The Clerk of the Senate is directed to transmit a copy of this
14 Resolution to Senator Reginald Thomas for delivery to Mitch Barnhart.
